original_title: Nish Kumar - Ruminations on the Nature of Subjectivity
overview: Filmed exclusively for Soho Theatre's Home Collection.  Two-time Edinburgh Comedy Award nominee and host of The Mash Report, Nish Kumar presents a stand-up comedy show for people who like stand-up comedy shows by a man that does stand-up comedy.
title: Nish Kumar - Ruminations on the Nature of Subjectivity
